Template: ring/add-deb-source
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Do you want to update GNU Ring together with the rest of the system?
 GNU Ring can configure your system to include new versions of the Ring
 package together with the regular system upgrades.
 .
 If you agree, GNU Ring will install a file into /etc/apt/sources.list.d,
 so that the Ring package is upgraded to any available newer release
 as part of your regular system upgrade.
